ign: left; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; mso-line-break-override: none; word-break: normal; punctuation-wrap: hanging;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"mso-special-format: bullet; font-family: Arial;\">&bull;</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: black;\">Step 6: Engage Learners</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"language: en-ID; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: .31in; text-indent: -.31in; text-align: left; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; mso-line-break-override: none; word-break: normal; punctuation-wrap: hanging;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"mso-special-format: bullet; font-family: Arial;\">&bull;</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: black;\">Step 7: Regular Assessment and Feedback</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"language: en-ID; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: .31in; text-indent: -.31in; text-align: left; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; mso-line-break-override: none; word-break: normal; punctuation-wrap: hanging;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"mso-special-format: bullet; font-family: Arial;\">&bull;</span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: black;\">Step 8: Encourage Continuous Learning</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"language: en-ID; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: .31in; text-indent: -.31in; text-align: left; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; mso-line-break-override: none; word-break: normal; punctuation-wrap: hanging;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: black;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></div>', 1, '2023-07-24 22:15:05', '2023-08-10 15:13:58');
INSERT INTO `solutions` (`id`, `title`, `subtitle`, `image`, `icon`, `slogan`, `banner`, `footer`, `detail`, `is_show`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES (6, 'e-Content Workshop & Consultation', 'Not only develop e-learning content (e-content) for you, but we will also help you to be able develop your own e-content', 'p7T6MIWCIWeqAJZco9YWbLi78xxuEANJY2EVjUIG.jpg', 'fa fa-compass', '\"We need to bring learning to people, instead of bring people to learning.\" Anonymous', 'fNi8N8mtsFdqgxwIjJzU5Fd9QCnvE2lIw0FMV65t.png', 'If you want to become an expert in developing e-content ......', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">In terms of expertise for developing e-content, you should need several skills, such as :</span></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Expertise in compiling instructional design and storyboarding</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Ability to compose content base on VAK (Visual, Auditory, Kinestatic)</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Understand the concept of ADDIE (Analyse, Design, Develop, Implement, Evaluate)</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Expert use of various design and authoring tools</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">In Wahana Tatar, we will unlock the secrets how to create e-content that will give optimum of learning absorption</span></p>', 1, '2023-07-24 22:17:57', '2023-08-16 03:50:58');
